Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.95,0:00:55.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko! Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.09,0:01:01.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.99,0:01:08.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This blizzard of leaves isn't\nfair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't try to get rid of me\nand go off by yourself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.10,0:01:16.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have express orders from\NHis Majesty and Maria.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.04,0:01:18.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're the heiress\nof the Mido family...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.84,0:01:20.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...following your clan's ancient\ntraditions...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you must still go to college\nlike a normal woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me, Miko?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.28,0:01:28.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.\NJust shut up for a minute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.89,0:01:31.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get back to my classes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.06,0:01:36.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First I want to try the secret\nleaf reading.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Read the leaves?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.23,0:01:41.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's a secret!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even tell me?\NNot fair!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.94,0:01:50.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can I look out for you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...unless you tell me\neverything?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''Predictions about\nfirst love''?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't look!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be\nembarrassed about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know a thing\nabout a woman's feelings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true, but still...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.86,0:02:13.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that incident with\nmy grandma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I've been stuck in the\NShikima Realm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...living a life of perversion.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.77,0:02:19.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had time to enjoy\nmy life as a woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but that's your fate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.21,0:02:26.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a woman after all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I experience first\nlove at least once or twice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First love is just once.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.61,0:02:35.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't nit-pick! Get off my\nback and quit bugging me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do this since I got\nback from the Shikima realm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:51.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It says that I'm about to meet\nthe man of my dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm choking! Miko, are you\nsure it doesn't mean me?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.51,0:03:02.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could you possibly be\nthe man of my dreams?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What on earth is this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Miko?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You keep sighing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got a crush on someone, huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing, Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So who is it? Just tell me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.18,0:04:13.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I promise not to tell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you're wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gossiping about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko says she's fallen in love!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to hide!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough looking for love\nlike this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else at college\nseems to have someone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even find someone I like,\nlet alone love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even my leaf divination\ntrick isn't coming true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!\NI'm gonna get drenched!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna get up?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That rain sure was sudden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it's gonna\nlet up, either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just coming to get you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just when things were\ngoing great.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's my little brother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Loves to play ninja.\NHe's such a handful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens\nwhen you play rough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where does it hurt? You'll be fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'm all right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go wait for me upstairs.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like,\NI can lend you this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd feel bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.74,0:06:23.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you need it, and\nwe have lots upstairs anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please take it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here, really.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll borrow it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let this package here\nget wet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you can bring it\nback any time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll bring it back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's your apartment\nnumber?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Room 901 . I'm Miko Mido.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hidemasa Matsunaga. I go\nto Tensho University.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.78,0:07:03.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After I've dropped this scroll\noff to a client...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring back your umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a scroll in there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I appraise antiques, just as my\ndeceased father did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It might seem like a weird\ninterest for someone my age.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it's wonderful!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.34,0:07:24.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me, going on\nabout myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.47,0:07:27.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry and\nget out of those wet clothes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to catch a cold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you, Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sanae? Aren't you finished\nchanging yet?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sanae?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's taking you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:58.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's so good!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.46,0:09:25.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you\neven more pleasure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to me now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro! I'm coming to you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nin-Nin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just heard a flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.78,0:10:24.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where? What? You're just\nimagining things, Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's strange.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.43,0:10:34.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late for college.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if we have\nany good antiques in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.77,0:10:39.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Antiques?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:43.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so I can get Hidemasa\nto appraise it for me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa?\NThat guy you met outside?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:46.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or else he'll just bring back\nthe umbrella...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I won't see him again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To think you've got the hots\nfor a pansy like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's the first guy who's\never made me feel this way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And considering that you\nalready have me here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sulking about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with\nme falling in love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know this is love?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.86,0:11:13.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's been going\npitter-patter since I met him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Let's see!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing,\nyou pervert!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your dirty hands off!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saving myself\nfor Hidemasa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you go find some\nkind of antique...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to help me with my\nfirst love?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right? Pretty please?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.03,0:11:43.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Well you've got nothing\nto be jealous about!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to lose my virginity to\nthe one I love...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...just like anybody else.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Virginity?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't help me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse to help me...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...then just stay out of my way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You faked crying!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.61,0:12:03.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If Hidemasa comes to return the\numbrella while I'm at college...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you dare accept it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take it myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin!\NJust pretend you're not home!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you,\nyou're late for college.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to have to\nwait until I get back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love, and I'm not going\nto let even you get in the way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what first love is like,\nso painful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.59,0:12:48.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was worried about me\ncatching a cold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he caught a cold himself\nand he's sick in bed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible, not being able\nto see him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.71,0:13:04.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kimie and Sanae skipped out.\NDo you know what's going on?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.85,0:13:05.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my own problems\nto think about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did the doorbell ring?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did Hidemasa come?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! You're back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here I thought you were\nstudying so hard...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but instead you've gone\nand fallen in love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.98,0:13:36.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well uh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin! You blabber mouth!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be\nembarrassed about!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's he like?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can I meet him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this has nothing\nto do with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to steal him\naway from you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How far have you gotten\nwith him? A kiss? Or...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that at all.\NI just lent him my umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.68,0:14:15.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of me. What'd\nyou come here for, anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got so wrapped up in\NNin-Nin's jealousy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that I completely forgot\nwhat I came for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Anti-Shikima?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Many strange things have\nbeen going on in the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.77,0:14:34.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maria says that it's a sign of\nthe Anti-Shikima's curse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard\nof the Anti-Shikima?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on in\nthe Shikima realm?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darling! What's happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!\NGet a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A strange flute has been\nsounding throughout the realm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the flute...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...has been affecting his\nphallus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flute strangely resounds\nthrough the Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:20.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and forebodes the revived hatred\nof the Anti-Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...stemming from an incident\nthat happened 400-years-ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Four hundred years ago\nwould mean...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The middle of the warring\nstates period!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.99,0:15:31.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow that haunting flute\nwas recently discovered.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.73,0:15:34.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's played in this world,\nits power is amplified...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...causing psychic activity in\nthe Shikima realm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's been causing\NHis Majesty's suffering.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:44.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's the same\nflute that I heard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was\nmy imagination.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you noticed any\nstrange things happening?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so caught up in your\nfirst love...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that you don't notice these\nthings anymore?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.25,0:16:01.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For once, I was just trying to\nbe a normal college student...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's all I've been\nthinking about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.36,0:16:06.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki! You mustn't be\nso hard on Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know I might have been\njealous...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:13.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's not like I don't\nunderstand how you feel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really Nin-Nin? Thank you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.84,0:16:23.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hidemasa Matsunaga.\NWould Miko Mido be in?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's him! What should I do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:31.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're so flustered?\NYou're hilarious!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.Just a moment.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since when are you so bashful?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.33,0:16:46.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've been waiting for\nhim all this time!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, what should I do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well hello!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.98,0:17:03.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.19,0:17:08.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this as a small\ntoken of my appreciation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was lend you\nmy umbrella.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to you, I kept that\npackage from getting wet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was valuable, so I really\nappreciated it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please, accept this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't make a big deal\nabout it. It's really nothing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you open it up?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Chidori incense urn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has quite a history.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve something\nso valuable.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.63,0:17:48.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop by another place,\nso I'd better be on my way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's great, Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to\ndo to me, Fubuki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what a nice urn it is!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's the first time a\nman's given me a present.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't want him,\NI'd sure take him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.33,0:18:23.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Think I'm going\nto steal him away from you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just might!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you if\nyou do!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so mad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we really\nhave to find out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...what's up with the\NAnti-Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:40.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to put that love\nof yours on the back burner.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin! Don't take your\neyes off Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.82,0:18:48.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have work to do, but we'll\nstill have to watch her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! Anything for you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My one chance to see\NHidemasa again...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.94,0:19:04.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I wasn't able to get\nany further with him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki! What's going on?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.67,0:19:41.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the flute!\NIt's burning me up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to Miko?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko? Are you all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki! Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.68,0:20:23.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were being assaulted\nby a hideous old ghost!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the strange sound\nof a flute in the bath...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and this weird sensation\ncame over my body.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.70,0:20:40.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't the only one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It happened to me, too!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the female flute\nof the Anti-Shikima!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Female flute?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maria said there's a\nfemale flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.84,0:20:52.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It responds to the male flute\nthat's been torturing the King.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, the flute makes\na strange, intoxicating sound...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that brings forth an amorous\nrapture in virginal women.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But for the Queen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the sound of the flute\ncauses unbearable pain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.76,0:21:07.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the sound of that flute\njust now, Maria was...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Maria!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The effect must've been\namplified in the Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.74,0:21:24.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and no doubt caused her\ngreat suffering!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.25,0:21:27.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't get the flutes\nback from the Anti-Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.75,0:21:30.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't save Mother and\NFather from their suffering!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.95,0:21:31.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how are we going to find\nthis Anti-Shikima?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flutes are steeped in an\nancient curse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.13,0:21:43.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko. Hidemasa is familiar\nwith antiques.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'd know\nanything about this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know\nwhere he lives.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about his university?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tensho University.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.74,0:21:54.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be nobody there\nat this hour.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.98,0:21:58.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance then!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find out his address\nfrom the university!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.48,0:22:02.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.19,0:22:11.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must be that estate\nover there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.96,0:22:15.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He sure lives in a big place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.97,0:22:22.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, what are you so\ntense about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.37,0:22:23.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about your crush\non him for now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.84,0:22:25.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save the Shikima\nand His Majesty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.01,0:22:27.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of\nmy relationship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.81,0:22:33.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as he finds out I'm the\nthe Shikima King's daughter...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.08,0:22:36.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he won't want anything\nto do with me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:42.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.73,0:22:48.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?\NThe food lady?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.96,0:22:52.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. It's me, Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:54.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.14,0:22:57.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa! Are you sick?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.21,0:23:02.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been feeling well\nsince last night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.04,0:23:06.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NAnd what's with that get-up?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.21,0:23:08.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have our reasons.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.12,0:23:12.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.49,0:23:16.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lady who brings me my\nmeals isn't here yet...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I can offer you\nsome tea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother, you're too sick!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.93,0:23:26.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.87,0:23:31.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know this might seem like\nan odd thing to ask.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.57,0:23:37.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of a 400-year-old\nlegend about a flute?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.18,0:23:41.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean the male and\nfemale flutes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.55,0:23:44.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You know about them!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.32,0:23:47.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I was cleaning up\nthe storehouse...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.55,0:23:49.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I stumbled across\none of them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.66,0:23:51.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I only found the male flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to play it, but I heard\nanother flute...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.83,0:23:59.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as if it were answering.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd feel sharp chest pains...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.10,0:24:04.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so I stopped playing it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.34,0:24:06.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And then I heard the\nother flute calling me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.04,0:24:08.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The female flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.38,0:24:09.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.61,0:24:11.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.11,0:24:16.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found an old book that\ndescribed the male flute...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.08,0:24:20.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and mentioned the existence\nof another flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.29,0:24:24.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how come you know\nabout those flutes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.33,0:24:27.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I might as well\ntell you the whole story.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.14,0:24:37.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same flute\nfrom last night!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.48,0:24:43.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That weird flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.78,0:24:51.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.93,0:25:07.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko! Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.94,0:25:12.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.96,0:25:32.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.36,0:25:39.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro! I love you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.97,0:25:42.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.34,0:25:46.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, my Kyoshiro?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.67,0:25:49.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will take revenge on\nthe Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.44,0:25:54.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to life,\nmy beloved Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.65,0:26:00.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Awake! Awake!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.39,0:26:09.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who calls me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.13,0:26:14.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who calls me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.50,0:26:44.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.00,0:26:49.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Know the depths of my\nkarmic suffering!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.24,0:26:51.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.44,0:26:53.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?!
